headline: Beyond Meat (BYND) Reports Q2 Loss, Lags Revenue Estimates
summary: Beyond Meat (BYND) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -16.22% and -8.31%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
